      "content": "you make it sound like the pain is the only thing i have left. but honestly, it just feels like a weight. i look at my life and i don't see a future, i just see a long, empty road that i'm forced to walk alone. sometimes i wonder if there's even a reason to keep walking it if the person i was walking it with is gone. it feels like i'm just holding onto nothing.",
